    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound 2004 BMW M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies. This example is equipped with the desirable 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a variable M differential lock for optimal power delivery. Significant preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS unit overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure chassis longevity. The suspension geometry is maintained via refreshed bushings and Bilstein B6 dampers, preserving the E46's renowned handling characteristics. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the drivetrain remains robust with linear power delivery and a crisp 8,000 RPM redline. A true driver\u2019s car with sorted internals and documented service history.",
