      "description": "This well-maintained sedan offers a perfect balance of performance and comfort. The exterior retains a high-gloss finish, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front bumper consistent with careful highway use. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and odor-free; the premium leather seats are supple, with only light creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. Every feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the touchscreen navigation system, functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this vehicle is sound, having followed a strict synthetic oil change schedule every 5,000 miles. The tires have plenty of tread remaining, and the brakes provide firm, responsive stopping power. It drives straight and true, offering a quiet, composed ride. Included are two sets of keys, the original owner's manual, and a full set of all-weather floor mats.",
      "price": 33850.0,
