    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s been absolute gold to me. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014super reliable, clean inside, and drives like a dream! It\u2019s been well-loved and carefully looked after, making it the perfect companion for your daily commutes or weekend getaways. If you\u2019re looking for a dependable car that still looks great on the road, this is the one for you. Come take it for a spin!",
