    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s specification, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six and a tactile 6-speed manual transmission. The powertrain remains robust, delivering a linear power band and a sharp 8,000 RPM redline. It is equipped with a factory limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal torque distribution across the rear axle. Recent technical attention includes a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul and a valve clearance adjustment to maintain peak volumetric efficiency. The chassis exhibits great rigidity, and the suspension maintains its communicative geometry for precise turn-in. While the finish shows minor patina from regular enjoyment, the mechanical vitals and subframe integrity make this a turn-key performance machine for the discerning enthusiast.",
